data.description: CUSTOM BUILT IN 2022 – Beautifully nestled in Goodsons Place, this home leaves no detail unattended. Situated on a private acre lot, modern character and charm abound in this like-new 3 bed, 2-1/2 bath executive home. The beauty this home exudes is apparent. Stately french doors extend a warm welcome, which is magnified by 20' ceilings and open concept living.  Expansive windows and doors throughout beam natural light. Relax with nature or entertain on the covered back deck.  The serenity this home offers is undeniable. While the main level captures open concept living, you will enjoy generous prep space with a stately kitchen island, mud room with deep sink, guest half bath, bonus room and garage with workshop area. A split bedroom plan with dual entry bath compliments the character. Tarry to the owner’s suite with the privacy of your own sitting area and spacious bath w/separate vanities, tile shower and two walk in closets. Convenience is key - minutes from Hwy 16 & 150. A MUST SEE!
